                                    <label for="drawer-19092025-jerome-noetinger-lionel-fernandez" class="drawer-button font-mono text-xs">
                                        • <a class="cursor-pointer hover:underline hover:decoration-dashed">Jérôme Noetinger ⨯ Lionel Fernandez</a> •
